        <Parent_String>place spoons [300207615], utensils for consuming food [300200039], culinary equipment for serving and consuming food [300200051], culinary equipment [300199765], equipment by context [300239170], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
